      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via at least one benchmark test case with known analytical solution.",
      "rationale": "Code verification confirmed against lid-driven cavity and Poiseuille flow benchmarks. Numerical errors are within expected truncation error bounds for second-order discretization."
    },
    {
