      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported for the primary QoI (hemolysis index) using at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three mesh levels (3.2M, 7.8M, 18.4M cells) were evaluated. GCI for hemolysis index is 4.1% on the fine mesh, satisfying the MRL 2 threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirms monotonic convergence."
