      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted at 3 L/min and 4500 RPM, 5 L/min and 3500 RPM, and 6 L/min and 3000 RPM — all within the CPB operating envelope. Temperature, blood analog viscosity, and hematocrit are documented."
