      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoI used in the model (hemolysis index derived from scalar shear stress and exposure time) must be directly mappable to the clinical acceptance criterion (RH < 1).",
      "rationale": "The model QoI is the normalized index of hemolysis, which is directly used to compute the relative hemolysis ratio RH against the predicate device. The mapping is explicit and documented in the analysis plan."
