    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Uncertainty quantification via comprehensive Monte Carlo sampling across all model inputs has been completed and the 95th-percentile NIH prediction interval remains below the RH < 1 acceptance threshold. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
